reviewText: The CD's were excellent, A little told side of WW II.

My father was a fleet tug sailor and I always wanted to know and feel more about it.  I was thrilled to find that someone had done work on the subject.  What I received in the mail was about five times more than I expected.  This is a stone solid reference for all who are interested in history and contains information that might well have been lost.  I couldn't believe how much material I got for the price.  ATF-75
The videos are well made and focus on the men who served on the tugs during the war years.  The book is excellent and an good supplement to the videos.
